{"tid":330473,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"脫墨後嘅護理","createTime":"2017-07-21T08:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T06:59:18.000Z","uid":130056,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"edfb933f14d4ec84696e9b63ff58dac7070aa2b1","tid":330473,"uid":130056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<br />\n琴日去左脫墨<br />\n粒墨本身唔算大 但都ok深 <br />\n醫生幫我用co2 laser做<br />\n脫完之後佢都有用酒精棉幫我消毒 再痴膠布<br />\n想問下咁多位有做過激光脫墨嘅巴絲 <br />\n膠布係咪要日日換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又聽人講話膠布會焗住傷口 甚至可能換膠布個陣整甩埋塊焦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  影響傷口<br />\n因為粒墨都生係塊面嘅當眼處 所以都驚會留疤 <br />\n唔知有冇人解答到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eee5d4c704d087ef4760ce62963019dcda3a620","tid":330473,"uid":130056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"a14b812dc11a9cb19260a839929fd0cb75f2d6fa","tid":330473,"uid":1144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"係邊到做 同做左幾多錢?"},{"pid":"803f05a15162fbc83b00037b19b8b6400bec8e8a","tid":330473,"uid":33832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"我早個排脫左，冇幫我痴膠布，<br />\n我覺得唔痴會好啲，乾爽啲快啲結焦快啲好<br />\n膠布貼足全日都唔好啦，<br />\n好易發炎"},{"pid":"1d4a9881bbd29f027f13543444df946137f44b7b","tid":330473,"uid":64050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:09:03.000Z","msg":"個陣激完連膠布都無<br />\n不過真係唔好嫌塊焦樣衰或者就甩就多手整走佢 同埋唔好食咁多刺激性既野 如果唔係就會有手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6366b2862abc82b77bf7fe05449a4f8ff8000b46","tid":330473,"uid":130056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我早個排脫左，冇幫我痴膠布，<br />\n我覺得唔痴會好啲，乾爽啲快啲結焦快啲好<br />\n膠布貼足全日都唔好啦，<br />\n好易發炎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次換膠布個陣都好驚自己會整到傷口 影響佢結焦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   最驚自己meet 甩焦會留疤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都已經兩日 唔再痴膠布應該都ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00029479d630634a9cd9a4102d97c202d25d0c5","tid":330473,"uid":130056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係邊到做 同做左幾多錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍾xx醫生 <br />\n$2500"},{"pid":"04149128b4d9f352f3164935a45ebca04796e895","tid":330473,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係邊到做 同做左幾多錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍾xx醫生 <br />\n$2500</blockquote><br />\n咁平，好耐之前我脫要五千。"},{"pid":"1496b8467b9feb46f3ebefd375ee12b52662c1cc","tid":330473,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣激完連膠布都無<br />\n不過真係唔好嫌塊焦樣衰或者就甩就多手整走佢 同埋唔好食咁多刺激性既野 如果唔係就會有手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋避免接觸太陽。"},{"pid":"bd5837e092e3ee380ccc74de3c659a4281017529","tid":330473,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講下背景先<br />\n琴日去左脫墨<br />\n粒墨本身唔算大 但都ok深 <br />\n醫生幫我用co2 laser做<br />\n脫完之後佢都有用酒精棉幫我消毒 再痴膠布<br />\n想問下咁多位有做過激光脫墨嘅巴絲 <br />\n膠布係咪要日日換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又聽人講話膠布會焗住傷口 甚至可能換膠布個陣整甩埋塊焦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  影響傷口<br />\n因為粒墨都生係塊面嘅當眼處 所以都驚會留疤 <br />\n唔知有冇人解答到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都唔會有疤，同埋如果粒墨較深就可能需要幾次去清，因為頭一兩次清完看似已脫，但之後墨既黑色素又會出返，但當然已比之前細好多。"},{"pid":"2f106c107e7e1e75c32152558105635e7ede0d44","tid":330473,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係邊到做 同做左幾多錢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍾xx醫生 <br />\n$2500</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2500係包d乜？<br />\n定係脫一粒2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe46b559290bfdd268584c1ade11ff76b12a1de8","tid":330473,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"早幾日試左D上網方法<br />\n用酸既果汁茶下<br />\n之後甩左D皮 淺色左<br />\n再之後用棉花簽點D醋 再點去粒墨到 一路點到佢痛痛地(同時粒墨會變白左) 用夾夾走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fa9c2698ad62a5cf384d8fd4209d98a5492709","tid":330473,"uid":62734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日試左D上網方法<br />\n用酸既果汁茶下<br />\n之後甩左D皮 淺色左<br />\n再之後用棉花簽點D醋 再點去粒墨到 一路點到佢痛痛地(同時粒墨會變白左) 用夾夾走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心？<br />\n我都想脱墨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c365763db981d1865023eff8ce93c133b08f17","tid":330473,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日試左D上網方法<br />\n用酸既果汁茶下<br />\n之後甩左D皮 淺色左<br />\n再之後用棉花簽點D醋 再點去粒墨到 一路點到佢痛痛地(同時粒墨會變白左) 用夾夾走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心？<br />\n我都想脱墨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結左焦<br />\n忍唔到手meet左 而家係組織液乾左個隻色(生得暗瘡多 而又手痕未熟就擠 擠到損 然後又忍唔到手成日meet個結焦既巴打應該明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 即係小小啡<br />\n遲下再用埋除疤膏 應該可以無事<br />\n係唔知夾走個下有無夾晒墨d野走 <br />\n怕番發 但而家睇落唔覺入面有黑色"},{"pid":"06230b2fcd9c34d30fa01417115215af28b03bf7","tid":330473,"uid":56878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早幾日試左D上網方法<br />\n用酸既果汁茶下<br />\n之後甩左D皮 淺色左<br />